<p align="center">The Le Dain Commission Report </p>

<h2><a name="DDE_LINK4">The Report of the Canadian Government
Commission of Inquiry into the Non-Medical Use of Drugs </a></h2>

<hr>

<p>This report, the largest study ever conducted by the
Government of Canada, is coming soon to these pages. </p>

