<p><b>BY ELLEN N. LA MOTTE</b> </p>

<p>AUTHOR OF &quot; BACKWASH OF WAR...... PEKING DUST,
CIVILIZATION,&quot; ETC. </p>

<p>THE MACMILLAN COMPANY - 1920 </p>

<hr>

<p>&quot; If this was our battle, if these were our ends, </p>

<p>Which were our enemies, which were our friends?&quot; </p>

<p>Witter Bynner, in The Nation. </p>

