<p>Appendix B. Great Men Who Have Used Drugs William Rowan
Hamilton, physicist Richard Feynman, physicist Sigmund Freud,
social scientist Samuel Taylor Coleridge, poet and critic William
Halsted, physician and educator, founder of Johns Hopkins Medical
